{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A multiplayer FPS shooter game, with multiple game modes. You have to use your voice to see the other players, otherwise you only see dark. Your weapons only working, when you are really LOUD. You can play this game, only when your microphone is on. Voice chat guaranteed!<br> ;)  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>KEY FEATURES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>MUTE =&gt; INVISIBLE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324800/extras/WalkInDarkSmall.gif?t=1732274756\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you are not making a noise, you are invisible to the other players.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">They can only see/hear you footsteps, when you are running.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>SHOUT =&gt; SEE AND SHOOT</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324800/extras/CatchWithSoundWaveSmall.gif?t=1732274756\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you make a sound, you create a soundwave.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With the soundwave, you can see the environemnt around you, and also the other players's outlines.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The louder you are, the farer you can see.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can make noise with your <u><strong>microphone</strong></u>.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>LOUDER =&gt; BETTER</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324800/extras/SoundSensitiveness.gif?t=1732274756\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">All of the guns has a volume threshold, that you have to reach to shoot with it.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The louder you are, the more accurate your weapon is.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>MULTIPLAYER</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Voice chat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Multiple maps</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Multiple unique, voice controlled weapons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Multiple game modes: Battleroyale, PVP, TDM, Capture the flag, Hide and seek</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Customizable characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">No microtransactions</p></li></ul>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3324800?t=1732274756","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3324800?t=1732274756","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324800/7959efc5329c3c4b76715bd163d0a001255b065e/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1732274756","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324800/7959efc5329c3c4b76715bd163d0a001255b065e/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1732274756","categories":[{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38},{"description":"Cross-Platform Multiplayer","id":27},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Captions available","id":13}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<h1>Discord Community</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324800/extras/JoinDiscord.gif?t=1732274756\" /></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A multiplayer FPS shooter game, with multiple game modes. You have to use your 